调到这里： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="“没关系”  - 最后一个晚宴（直播在晚会上）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/3W52NFb1s5M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，上一场晚宴的第一个录音室唱片将包含单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-new-single-sinner-uk-tour-radar-3463558">“罪人”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-share-new-single-my-lady-of-mercy-3511842">“我的仁慈女士”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">“在您身边”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-last-dinner-partys-empowering-new-single-caesar-on-a-tv-screen-3565601">“电视屏幕上的凯撒”</a> 。 <em>NME</em>最近在其 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/2024-albums-billie-eilish-green-day-3562749">“ 2024年最受期待的专辑发行”列表</a>中包括了LP。</p><p>同时，“没关系”在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-songs-of-2023-3-3551141">上个月的<em>NME&#39;50</em>最佳歌曲</a>中排名第五。</p><p>在他们的英国人崛起之星获胜之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-sleaford-mods-keane-to-perform-for-brits-week-in-aid-of-war-child-3571507">最后一场晚宴将在三月份的英国周刊中进行特别表演</a>。一次性演出系列将在《战争儿童的帮助》中进行。</p><p>本月初， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-crowned-bbc-sound-of-2024-winners-3565767">乐队被冠以BBC Radio 1的2024年民意调查的冠军</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-intimate-variety-show-at-london-roundhouse-buy-tickets-3507689">最后一场晚宴将在首张专辑发行的前夕（2月1日）在伦敦的Roundhouse举行标题表演</a>。该组织以前嘲笑演出“可能是历史”。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-last-dinner-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F5395177" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里找到剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>然后，他们将前往一系列英国唱片商店的日期，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-2024-european-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3531799">开始进行欧洲巡回演出</a>。 TLDP还将在2024年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-announce-stacked-line-up-for-2024-3545261">Primavera Sound</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-and-dua-lipa-announced-as-rock-werchter-2024-headliners-3537761">Rock Werchter</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2024-line-up-lana-del-rey-tyler-the-creator-doja-cat-no-doubt-3571866">Coachella</a>露面。</p><p>邮报<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-last-dinner-party-make-their-us-tv-debut-with-blistering-performance-nothing-matters-nme-radar-3573104">观看了最后一场晚宴，使他们的电视台首次亮相，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
